==== Train slope steepness====
Sets the steepness of slopes, trains will slow down more on slopes if this setting is set to a higher value. It only applies if the [[Main/en/realistic acceleration]] is selected.

;Valid options<nowiki>:</nowiki> [0 <= n <= 10]
: 0: 0% (lowest)
: ...
: <span style="color:blue">'''3: 3% (default)'''</span>
: ...
: 10: 10% (steepest)

